name: Gather Community Plant #015 - Poppel
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from Tezos artists and their artistic renditions of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Poppel is an GIS technician, writer/journalist who is interested in computer culturescape and art.

"Metaphorically saying I’m not afraid to walk long straight roads but twisted and winding alleys. Not having an idea is like being trapped and lost in those alleys, it grinds down my soul and makes me groan in pain. " - Poppel
